Render the introduction vignette in the `vignettes/` directory and save to
`inst/` folder as HTML which the link is used in the README file:

```
rmarkdown::render(
  input = "vignettes/writing-unit-tests-with-hamcrest.Rmd",
  output_file = "writing-unit-tests-with-hamcrest.html",
  output_dir = "inst"
)
```

